aggregation: An average mean of indicators focused on election suffrage in practice for men(v2elmalsuf) and women (v2elfemsuf).
clarification: Legal voting rights can be compromised by a number of issues for example intimidation, insecurity, prohibitive laws or practices, impersonation, or by social/religious norms and practices. Do not consider registration practices that place the burden on the voter to take action to register ahead of the election.
